{"tid":2200572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳秋實週四9月17日將釋放","createTime":"2020-09-13T05:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T06:00:48.000Z","uid":313615,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"877aec87c9a190ecbf1d1aeb108b17b901aed020","tid":2200572,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:18:40.000Z","msg":"消息來源內地國保"},{"pid":"7965f2403816ada91f98a80c723180b3aba0207e","tid":2200572,"uid":17641,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:20:11.000Z","msg":"連登仔：鬼嚟，共產黨放佢出嚟分化香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2ab9dfd791581e6b185e47892e275edd4e9f53","tid":2200572,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:20:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">一齊google畀零分比香島中學 等啲家長揀嘅時候會考慮清楚</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n之前我地<span class=\"purple\"><strong>過百留言一一被delete</strong></span>，估計被google評為無效，請繼續追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">香島中學<br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/rpGUKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FrpGUKs&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513XjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=bde4650a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/rpGUKs</a><br />\n天水圍香島中學<br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/eNAKtm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FeNAKtm&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513XjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=e75f178f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/eNAKtm</a><br />\n將軍澳香島中學 <br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/C9Vm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FC9Vm&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513XjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=18ea82e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/C9Vm</a></span>Z3<br />\n<br />\n留言:<br />\n事件一<br />\n校方帶頭將政治帶入校園，一名教師懷疑在音樂考試時未有禁止學生演奏「不恰當歌曲」而不獲續約。<br />\n<br />\n事件二<br />\n香島中學正校關注組指，9月7日一名中四學生突然被校長及訓導主任召回學校會面，校方指該名同學在網上溝通軟件Microsoft Team的簡介上填寫了抗爭口號，因而作出處分，包括立即停學一個星期，並向教育局通報。校方向該名學生表示，若然希望保留學位則需要記兩個大過，及警告再有發現參與社會運動，將會立即開除學籍。<br />\n<br />\n關注組成員又提到，校方曾多次警告該名學生不要參與社會活動，否則後果自負等；又指校方「敕令停課」的處分嚴重，形容是關注組成立後至今最嚴重的處分，指校方從未有處分關注組的成員或對抗校方的同學，故對校方處分「平平無奇」的學生感到詫異。"},{"pid":"3c74e454421853bc743f37871888dcb56bcd9962","tid":2200572,"uid":153151,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:21:04.000Z","msg":"見到啲人聽隻支那豬講嘢真係好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26c7727247921faae4cee8392279af242ecdefb","tid":2200572,"uid":68746,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"放完出嚟一定變得好愛國"},{"pid":"f5a6d89b3928cce2d9d57cdddb92989d703eed3f","tid":2200572,"uid":261849,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:27:33.000Z","msg":"放出嚟仲識唔識拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1545426cc9cb2f77da034cc94d6de5fc90d303a2","tid":2200572,"uid":309553,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:30:35.000Z","msg":"坐完變真大外宣"},{"pid":"c123fa24d8e0315d8e355fc8a82ee613ed032990","tid":2200572,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:30:54.000Z","msg":"被喂食完懵仔丸了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c528e195d0b04698346c9b1599ea9ae38ac6ce9c","tid":2200572,"uid":372390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:31:18.000Z","msg":"中左武肺都唔死得<br />\n條友真係大命"},{"pid":"7fedc9fc0f5fafa15d543f03478504802215159b","tid":2200572,"uid":238747,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:31:28.000Z","msg":"係就好，最緊要人無事"}